     isolated from Ectothiorhodospira halophila determined at 2.5-A
     resolution."
     J. Biol. Chem. 266:18660-18667(1991).
     PubMed=1917989
[ 2] Kusano T., Takeshima T., Sugawara K., Inoue C., Shiratori T., Yano T.,
