     PubMed=1317860
[ 3] Van Driessche G., Vandenberghe I., Devreese B., Samyn B., Meyer T.E.,
     Leigh R., Cusanovich M.A., Bartsch R.G., Fischer U.,
     Van Beeumen J.J.
